                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 99ra: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 99ra: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘጐይታና፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ መዝገበ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ስመ፡ እሙ፡ ወለተ፡ ማርያም፡ ስመ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ለተ፡ ሐይማኖት፡ ወደቂቁ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ቄስ፡ ገብረ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ገብረ፡ መድኅን፡ ገብረ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘተሳየጦ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ወወሃቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ በአቲ፡፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 99ra:This book is of gwäytana Gäbrä Maryam, his father's name is Mäzgäbä Śəllase, his mother name is Wälättä Maryam, his wife name is [Wä]lättä Haymanot, his children  Wälättä Michael, priest Gäbrä Ṣadqan, Gäbrä Krəstos, Gäbrä Mädḫən, Gäbrä Yoḥannəs. He has bought it with his money so that it might be his guide  to the Kingdom of Heaven, and donated it to the tabot of St. Michael Bäˀatti.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Writing exercises in the margins: fols. 8v, 28r, 29v, 48v, 49v, 82r, 99ra.&#xD;
- Space for rubricated names left unfilled in supplication formulas: fols. 16vb, 22va, 28rb, 33va, 35va, 44vb, 45ra-va, 70vb, 71va, 75rb, 80rb, 85ra, 87vb, 91vb, 92rb, 94va.&#xD;
- Words or passages erased: fols. 4r, 23rb.&#xD;
- Correction written interlineally: fols. 27vb, 36r, 44r.&#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script: fols. 26va-27vb, 40vb-51va, 53ra-53vb, 54vb-55va, 59ra-60rb, 65rb-65va, 68va-vb.&#xD;
- Lacunae: fols. 55va-vb, 63ra-rb.&#xD;
- Supplication of the scribe: fol. 99ra.</item>
